svg:g.svg:text: This prototype is the product of a semester thesis (Vertiefungsblockarbeit) at the Institute
of Cartography within the scope of my diploma course in Geomatics Engineering at the
Swiss Federal Institute of Technology (ETH) Zurich.
I'd like to thank A. Neumann and P. Sykora who supervised this thesis and helped me a lot.
Also many thanks to everyone who has supported this project with some photos.
For further information you may have a look into the technical report of the project.
